<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/12 (Thu.) Why do people love travelling? / How to celebrate Arbor Day. (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=370&amp;p=387#p387"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">*** Removal Notice ***<br />Thursday gathering of Royal Club is relocated to Ikari Coffee 怡客咖啡, 台北市中正區衡陽路116號<br /></span><br /><br />Session 1: Why do people love travelling?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://blog.virtuoso.com/tips-and-trends/10-powerful-reasons-why-people-love-to-travel/">https://blog.virtuoso.com/tips-and-tren ... to-travel/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1. Do you like to travel? Why or why not?<br />Q2. Share your travelling experience, the most unforgettable?<br />Q3. How do you like to travel, with tour group, independent travel, solo, long stay, cruise, backpack, -- – with whom?<br />Q4. Was there any bad memory about traveling?<br />Q5. What benefit do you gain the most from traveling?<br />Q6. Which country would you like to visit next time, why?<br />Extended reading:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.huffpost.com/entry/the-14-types-of-travel-ev_b_10193436">https://www.huffpost.com/entry/the-14-t ... b_10193436</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br />Session 2: How to celebrate Arbor Day<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.farmersalmanac.com/why-do-we-celebrate-arbor-day-3169">https://www.farmersalmanac.com/why-do-w ... r-day-3169</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1. How do we celebrate Arbor Day?<br />Q 2.What do you think trees can do for us?<br />Q3.How do you appreciate trees in your life?<br />Q4. Do you plant any trees at home? Why or why not?<br />Q5. How do you enjoy nature?<br /><br /><br />===================================================================<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 pm-7:30 pm Free talk<br />7:30 pm-8:10 pm Session 1 discussion<br />8:10 pm-8:40 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 pm-8:45 pm Break time &amp; Group picture<br />8:45 pm-9:15 pm Session 2 discussion<br />9:15 pm-9:30 pm Presentation<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Sat Mar 07, 2020 8:27 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
